  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Assistant Landscape Supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Requirement</strong></p>\n<p>· Ensure work tasks are completed on time.</p>\n<p>· Handle client questions on the landscape project.</p>\n<p>· Identify symptoms, pests and diseases.</p>\n<p>· Improve growing conditions using proper nutrient fertilisers and soil mix.</p>\n<p>· Manage landscape maintenance works.</p>\n<p>· Organise work orders with the ground crew.</p>\n<p>· Plan and ensure safety regulations are followed.</p>\n<p>· Plan daily work schedule for the workforce.</p>\n<p>· Review of the plant health, soil, water and other environmental conditions.</p>\n<p>· Review sites according to the health and safety regulations.</p>\n<p>· Always able to coordinate with and reported to Landscape Supervisor</p>\n<p>· Any other duties as assigned by immediate superior.</p>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<p>· Required language(s): English, Chinese (in order to deal with complaints from Chinese speaking client on site)</p>\n<p>· Dynamic and energetic</p>\n<p>· Good team player with ability to lead and multi-task</p>\n<p>· Committed to work</p>\n<p>· Required Skill(s): Microsoft Office</p>\n<p>· Excellent interpersonal and communication skills</p>\n<p>· Prefer candidates with horticulture or arborist knowledge</p>\n<p>· On-the-job training provided</p>\n<p>· Entry level candidates with the relevant Polytechnic / WSQ Diploma / Degree are welcomed</p>\n<p>Working Hours and Office Location:</p>\n<p>· 5.5-day work week</p>\n<p>· Office location: Mandai Estate</p>\n<p>· Work location: Various Sites</p>",
